<p class="ayah 25-25" style="font-family: 'KFGQPC Uthman Taha Naskh';"><span class=""><span class="word staticWord"><span class="ar quranText top first rtl" dir="rtl">وَيَوْمَ</span><span class="en second ltr" dir="ltr">And (the) Day</span></span><span class="word staticWord"><span class="ar quranText top first rtl" dir="rtl">تَشَقَّقُ</span><span class="en second ltr" dir="ltr">will split open</span></span><span class="word staticWord"><span class="ar quranText top first rtl" dir="rtl">ٱلسَّمَآءُ</span><span class="en second ltr" dir="ltr">the heavens</span></span><span class="word staticWord"><span class="ar quranText top first rtl" dir="rtl">بِٱلْغَمَـٰمِ</span><span class="en second ltr" dir="ltr">with the clouds</span></span><span class="word staticWord"><span class="ar quranText top first rtl" dir="rtl">وَنُزِّلَ</span><span class="en second ltr" dir="ltr">and (will be) sent down</span></span><span class="word staticWord"><span class="ar quranText top first rtl" dir="rtl">ٱلْمَلَـٰٓئِكَةُ</span><span class="en second ltr" dir="ltr">the Angels,</span></span><span class="word staticWord"><span class="ar quranText top first rtl" dir="rtl">تَنزِيلاً</span><span class="en second ltr" dir="ltr">descending.</span></span></span> <a href="#!/quran-wordbyword/25:25" class="ayahNumber" data-verse="2880"><span class="icon leftBracket"> </span>25<span class="icon rightBracket"> </span></a></p>
