<p class="ayah 25-27" style="font-family: 'KFGQPC Uthman Taha Naskh';"><span class=""><span class="word staticWord"><span class="ar quranText top first rtl" dir="rtl">وَيَوْمَ</span><span class="en second ltr" dir="ltr">And (the) Day</span></span><span class="word staticWord"><span class="ar quranText top first rtl" dir="rtl">يَعَضُّ</span><span class="en second ltr" dir="ltr">will bite</span></span><span class="word staticWord"><span class="ar quranText top first rtl" dir="rtl">ٱلظَّالِمُ</span><span class="en second ltr" dir="ltr">the wrongdoer</span></span><span class="word staticWord"><span class="ar quranText top first rtl" dir="rtl">عَلَىٰ</span><span class="en second ltr" dir="ltr">[on]</span></span><span class="word staticWord"><span class="ar quranText top first rtl" dir="rtl">يَدَيْهِ</span><span class="en second ltr" dir="ltr">his hands,</span></span><span class="word staticWord"><span class="ar quranText top first rtl" dir="rtl">يَقُولُ</span><span class="en second ltr" dir="ltr">he will say,</span></span><span class="word staticWord"><span class="ar quranText top first rtl" dir="rtl">يَـٰلَيْتَنِى</span><span class="en second ltr" dir="ltr">"O I wish!</span></span><span class="word staticWord"><span class="ar quranText top first rtl" dir="rtl">ٱتَّخَذْتُ</span><span class="en second ltr" dir="ltr">I had taken</span></span><span class="word staticWord"><span class="ar quranText top first rtl" dir="rtl">مَعَ</span><span class="en second ltr" dir="ltr">with</span></span><span class="word staticWord"><span class="ar quranText top first rtl" dir="rtl">ٱلرَّسُولِ</span><span class="en second ltr" dir="ltr">the Messenger</span></span><span class="word staticWord"><span class="ar quranText top first rtl" dir="rtl">سَبِيلاً</span><span class="en second ltr" dir="ltr">a way.</span></span></span> <a href="#!/quran-wordbyword/25:27" class="ayahNumber" data-verse="2882"><span class="icon leftBracket"> </span>27<span class="icon rightBracket"> </span></a></p>
