<p class="ayah 25-30" style="font-family: 'KFGQPC Uthman Taha Naskh';"><span class=""><span class="word staticWord"><span class="ar quranText top first rtl" dir="rtl">وَقَالَ</span><span class="en second ltr" dir="ltr">And said</span></span><span class="word staticWord"><span class="ar quranText top first rtl" dir="rtl">ٱلرَّسُولُ</span><span class="en second ltr" dir="ltr">the Messenger,</span></span><span class="word staticWord"><span class="ar quranText top first rtl" dir="rtl">يَـٰرَبِّ</span><span class="en second ltr" dir="ltr">"O my Lord!</span></span><span class="word staticWord"><span class="ar quranText top first rtl" dir="rtl">إِنَّ</span><span class="en second ltr" dir="ltr">Indeed,</span></span><span class="word staticWord"><span class="ar quranText top first rtl" dir="rtl">قَوْمِى</span><span class="en second ltr" dir="ltr">my people</span></span><span class="word staticWord"><span class="ar quranText top first rtl" dir="rtl">ٱتَّخَذُواْ</span><span class="en second ltr" dir="ltr">took</span></span><span class="word staticWord"><span class="ar quranText top first rtl" dir="rtl">هَـٰذَا</span><span class="en second ltr" dir="ltr">this</span></span><span class="word staticWord"><span class="ar quranText top first rtl" dir="rtl">ٱلْقُرْءَانَ</span><span class="en second ltr" dir="ltr">the Quran</span></span><span class="word staticWord"><span class="ar quranText top first rtl" dir="rtl">مَهْجُورًا</span><span class="en second ltr" dir="ltr">(as) a forsaken thing."</span></span></span> <a href="#!/quran-wordbyword/25:30" class="ayahNumber" data-verse="2885"><span class="icon leftBracket"> </span>30<span class="icon rightBracket"> </span></a></p>
