<p class="ayah 25-32" style="font-family: 'KFGQPC Uthman Taha Naskh';"><span class=""><span class="word staticWord"><span class="ar quranText top first rtl" dir="rtl">وَقَالَ</span><span class="en second ltr" dir="ltr">And said</span></span><span class="word staticWord"><span class="ar quranText top first rtl" dir="rtl">ٱلَّذِينَ</span><span class="en second ltr" dir="ltr">those who</span></span><span class="word staticWord"><span class="ar quranText top first rtl" dir="rtl">كَفَرُواْ</span><span class="en second ltr" dir="ltr">disbelieve,</span></span><span class="word staticWord"><span class="ar quranText top first rtl" dir="rtl">لَوْلَا</span><span class="en second ltr" dir="ltr">"Why not</span></span><span class="word staticWord"><span class="ar quranText top first rtl" dir="rtl">نُزِّلَ</span><span class="en second ltr" dir="ltr">was revealed</span></span><span class="word staticWord"><span class="ar quranText top first rtl" dir="rtl">عَلَيْهِ</span><span class="en second ltr" dir="ltr">to him</span></span><span class="word staticWord"><span class="ar quranText top first rtl" dir="rtl">ٱلْقُرْءَانُ</span><span class="en second ltr" dir="ltr">the Quran</span></span><span class="word staticWord"><span class="ar quranText top first rtl" dir="rtl">جُمْلَةً وَٲحِدَةً‌ۚ</span><span class="en second ltr" dir="ltr">all at once?"</span></span><span class="word staticWord"><span class="ar quranText top first rtl" dir="rtl">كَذَٲلِكَ</span><span class="en second ltr" dir="ltr">Thus,</span></span><span class="word staticWord"><span class="ar quranText top first rtl" dir="rtl">لِنُثَبِّتَ</span><span class="en second ltr" dir="ltr">that We may strengthen</span></span><span class="word staticWord"><span class="ar quranText top first rtl" dir="rtl">بِهِۦ</span><span class="en second ltr" dir="ltr">thereby</span></span><span class="word staticWord"><span class="ar quranText top first rtl" dir="rtl">فُؤَادَكَ‌ۖ</span><span class="en second ltr" dir="ltr">your heart,</span></spa